    @Model(adaptables=SlingHttpServletRequest.class,
       adapters={ResponsiveGrid.class,ComponentExporter.class},
       defaultInjectionStrategy=OPTIONAL,
       resourceType="wcm/foundation/components/responsivegrid")
public class ResponsiveGrid
extends AbstractResource
implements ResponsiveGridExporter
    Sling model for the Responsive grid component. A Responsive grid component provides access to its columns and generates a set of specific responsive data.
